entry.title: tripal/tripal
entry.summary: The Tripal package is a suite of Drupal modules for creating biological (genomic, genetic, breeding) websites. Visit the Tripal homepage at http://tripal.info for documentation, support, and other information. The Drupal project page is at http://drupal.org/project/tripal.
